ours at 00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC using a time-weighted average of the premium/discount between the perpetual price and mark price. The funding rate is capped at ±0.75% per interval to prevent extreme payments. Long positions pay shorts when funding is positive, and vice versa when negative, with payments occurring automatically at funding time."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
